data.name: label5.Text
data.value:
This will upload the files of your current project to the server as a library. Anyone can then download your library and use it with their code.
Some things to note: * Disabled files will not be uploaded * You need an account to finish the upload procedure * Once you upload a library, only you will be able to upload other libraries with the same name. * The name and version may not contain any of the following characters: /, \, <, >, :, ", |, ?, * * Any leading or trailing whitespace in the name or version will be removed.
